OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClearer
OL,6,Fskies for many overnight which will
OL,7,Fallow temperatures to fall, giving a
OL,8,Fmuch more comfortable night for many.
OL,9,FStaying dry with mist and fog in
OL,10,Fplaces.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA bright start under some
OL,13,Fhigh cloud, sunny spells turning hazy.
OL,14,FMore in the way of sunshine by the
OL,15,Fmiddle part of the afternoon. Staying
OL,16,Fvery warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
