OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,6,Fsees sunny spells and scattered
OL,7,Fshowers. Continuing into Monday with
OL,8,Fheavy rain, possible thunderstorms.
OL,9,FStaying unsettled through the week as
OL,10,Ftemperatures return to average.
